{"tid":713923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【$25萬12日】強國「神童班」學啲乜？ 虎爸媽谷囝囡臉吸匙羮","createTime":"2018-06-23T08:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T09:53:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e5765d35b1247242e5acef30727db7faf110e3e2","tid":713923,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529668297_784a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529668297_784a.jpg&h=038a0511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地虎爸虎媽為催谷子女，豪花20萬元人民幣（下同，約25萬港元）報讀「神功班」！湖南長沙網民「堂吉CG訶德」近日在微博爆料，在屋苑的微信群宣傳「學習班」，培訓孩童「全腦靈動」，激發人體潛能。宣傳照是一名女童能將4把匙羮「吸」在臉上，另一女童用額頭「控制」着手機，這些特異功能令網民笑謔：「2018年了，居然還有這種？」「要是能成仙，值！」<br />\n<br />\n繼續睇：<br />\n【$25萬神童班】囝囝蒙眼讀報紙識「透視」 家長信到十足！（<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ltNPgc）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ltNPgc%EF%BC%89&d=%2BbDes5M%2BhYKS2GX4MBi%2Bk6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=31417095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ltNPgc）</a><br />\n<br />\n內地記者前日（21日）聯絡到玄悟文化傳播有限公司宣傳該課程的何女士，她聲稱這個培訓班費用不便宜，4天課程費用3.98萬元（約4.8萬港元），12天課程就要20萬元。究竟匙羮「吸」臉又是甚麼原理？何女士回覆：「這只是本身能量的一個小呈現。上過全階段課的孩子還可以鼻子認字，手指摸字，耳朵聽字&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n何女士相約到「雨花區萬科&middot;金域華府」一處民房見面，她表示，課程是「培養孩子仁義禮智信，讓孩子們的潛力最大程度地運用起來」，招生對象為5至15歲學童。何女士還談論許多「心靈、精神、理念、能量」等詞彙，她表示孩童完成課程後相當於「從手動擋（汽車術語：棍波）換成了自動擋（自動波）」，自主地掌握一些事情，包括一些能困擾大人的，「我要選擇甚麼樣的專業、我要上哪個大學、找甚麼樣的對象結婚、生個有靈性的孩子&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n對於聽着相當玄妙的「鼻子認字」，何女士解釋：「感官都是可以相通的」。接着，她親身示範用額頭吸匙羮，她表示自己只需1秒鐘便可以做到，「主要是專注力和自信心，把自己想像成一塊吸鐵石。」至於如何做到，則需進行系統學習，讓學童懂得運用如何運用自身的能量。<br />\n<br />\n目前，湖南長沙雨花區工商部門已展開調查，執法人員將上門進行核實情況，是否涉嫌違規超過經營範圍、是否真的涉及詐騙行為，目前正在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180623/58350298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F58350298&d=%2BbDes5M%2BhYKS2GX4MBi%2Bk6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8be3f299\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F58350298&h=c35efb0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180623/58350298</a>"},{"pid":"59ba5fd163221e056b33ffa915c8b56dbaba23fd","tid":713923,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:49:00.000Z","msg":"香港個件係咪細個報咗呢個班"},{"pid":"dc125cd05d6cf7dec7012891176cfe2c0b9ba918","tid":713923,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:00:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">手指摸字，耳朵聽字</span><br />\n原來未上過係做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af1fe5adde39d73e661a7888873ab015bb572b7","tid":713923,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20141215/s00008/1435132914545_D62D6C0763072DD966DA65FFBD144C03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20141215%2Fs00008%2F1435132914545_D62D6C0763072DD966DA65FFBD144C03.jpg&h=19a2db42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da2c6178efde1e1ebffc7d66a3d3818cbc32356d","tid":713923,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:02:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n1jiaCITqfk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn1jiaCITqfk&d=%2BbDes5M%2BhYKS2GX4MBi%2Bk6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=216e8b3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n1jiaCITqfk</a>"},{"pid":"9525bf0b1a4a1a13ea363d54533378a5c00cacd7","tid":713923,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc125cd05d6cf7dec7012891176cfe2c0b9ba918","tid":713923,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:00:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">手指摸字，耳朵聽字</span><br />\n原來未上過係做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:04:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SPx92jSheiA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSPx92jSheiA&d=%2BbDes5M%2BhYKS2GX4MBi%2Bk6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=88d8c20e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SPx92jSheiA</a>"},{"pid":"f1904affd303ad6979f6c4d97dc63a1ee8d40b18","tid":713923,"uid":14423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:22:04.000Z","msg":"【蘋果踢爆】集體中伏！千人報考補習天王DSE模擬試 臨場開班教念力<br />\n2017-01-11370.1K<br />\n即時要聞<br />\n <br />\n補習社星河教育聯同慈善機構青年天地發展基金，上月舉辦中學文憑試模擬試（Mock exam），吸引近千DSE準考生參加；期間「補習天王」范浩揚（ K.OTen ）在場內推廣「蒙眼透視」及「皮膚吸附金屬」等訓練課程近1小時，更即場派發報名表。有考生坦言透過其就讀中學得悉模擬試詳情，報名參加後始知「中伏」；涉事中學回應指，事前不知道模擬試由私人補習社舉辦及包含有關訓練，對事件感擔憂，會輔導曾參加的學生。"},{"pid":"ce5650e28c1df0d89a5a2d62a121f74714deddf6","tid":713923,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:23:56.000Z","msg":"有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feae77edeaf516ac1468bcc8f3b115426098e6b5","tid":713923,"uid":179467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce5650e28c1df0d89a5a2d62a121f74714deddf6","tid":713923,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:23:56.000Z","msg":"有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:36:42.000Z","msg":"歡樂滿東華咪有用囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bafaecffa1a55b0cb82653e389b70ee8d2d20c","tid":713923,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce5650e28c1df0d89a5a2d62a121f74714deddf6","tid":713923,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:23:56.000Z","msg":"有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20